</taxonomicName>
, adult male from culture from Loeng Yai reservoir, Khon Kaen area: A—lateral view, B—postabdomen, C—antennule, D —thoracic limb I, E—copulatory hook and IDL of limb I. Scale bars: 0.1 mm for A, 0.05 mm for B–E.
</paragraph>
